  "description": "An awesome, fresh and colorful resource pack which brings to life the Overworld thanks to variant textures!",
  "body": "<center> \n\n![Olive's_Garden_Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/02ff0f58546bcba2d20ab33ac1bd82f18b22b8c0.jpeg)\n\n\n**Welcome to Olive's Garden!**\n\nTransform the entire Overworld like never before. Grass blocks, mycelium, flowers, and<br>plants have all been completely revamped and expanded with tons of vibrant new variants.<br>Every biome feels richer, fuller, way more natural and ~~olive~~ alive.\n\nJump in and explore the upgrade!\n\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/pixelforge\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/32237a5eb0e69b0cfb6f79b09d08bafae2139664.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/shadows_pixelforge\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f8e5473c7cc891773d0963a204a7dbc0cae6ab8.png\" alt=\"Ko-fi\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/QrU6QCFj5r\"> \n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab1d9434d86f69f02be997775cc20d9f968fc6a6.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fc15ed1de151999554a0a966e39ccaef439d6d4d.png\" alt=\"Twitch\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2f10668a84476def0faf37c42319e0222484f94d.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/c/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b10f11429c9b97af2b45fcda64792d815fdeb5fb.png\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/shadowspixelforge/projects\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6aa1b4a7d469617ce0e922b931c24e73ef48dc59.png\" alt=\"Curseforge\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3qlCr9lXguH44qq5xqAlzQ\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/74af846b0dabfde51cc50f295809ec96f63e26a2.png\" alt=\"Youtube\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://x.com/SPixelForge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eb699f87a889d2710efc5dcff9b6b023b2be2d58.png\" alt=\"X\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a>\n<br><br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/42766e53bc9dd64b67e6e56b98aa5f9532a9bd07.png\" alt=\"hr1\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a2f227dd350f4e2322f500900863b7a6696b74f7.png\" alt=\"NO DEPENDENCIES REQUIRED\" width=\"660\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n  **This resource pack works perfectly with Vanilla Minecraft - NO EXTRA MODS REQUIRED.** \n\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/521094f3dd8b6b35de94d6f0706e706104f94fa6.png\" alt=\"hr2\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c7f3b2837c699bc40bda584b7d5781389c4dbe3d.png\" alt=\"MORE INTERESTING PROJECTS\" width=\"690\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"20\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/the-night-of-the-living-pumpkins\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/243c0c1904de2361e931432a6e0e5b0ee6b27e8f.png\" alt=\"The Night of the Living Pumpkins Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      The Night of the <br> Living Pumpkins!\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/shadows-pixels-reforged\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81c5b3f05c13dac83081221b58110365ada040c7_0.webp\" alt=\"Shadow's Pixels Reforged Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Shadow's Pixels Reforged <br>\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/potion-recipes-dark-mode-edition!\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/179f7ae47e64e9c6003cc734d355f676e221a2b8.png\" alt=\"Potion Recipes: Dark Mode Edition Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Potion Recipes: <br> Dark Mode Edition\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cb9880b04c1ea0fa927cf2e520c04599b3f0598d.png\" alt=\"hr3\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f88863218a1c549051bc37c2cbd07a395d1bdd2.png\" alt=\"YOUR SUPPORT MAKES THE DIFFERENCE\" width=\"850\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\nIf you like the content I make, don’t hesitate to join my Patreon or Ko-fi to enjoy all the exclusive members-only content, you'll get access to a lot of bonus content like WIPs, making ofs, dev. blogs and much more!\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/shadows_pixelforge/tiers\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6dc8719629fd05f40aba4f4e58bc56458925abae.png\" alt=\"join ko-fi\" width=\"400\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/shadowspixelforge/membership\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e73a4a0852508cb8d2b6a3dae2a42baef09334c0.png\" alt=\"join patreon\" width=\"400\" height=\"50\"> </a> \n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/57ec55483b7577b4f413abe89b2701f77ad4b3bb.png\" alt=\"hr4\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fb424f5c7e4031e9d8691616a446883413c75421.png\" alt=\"FAQs\" width=\"155\" height=\"50\">\n\n</center>\n<br>\n<br>\n\nHere I leave some answers to a few possible questions you may have, I hope it can help you.\n\n<details>\n  <summary>Frequently Asked Questions</summary>\n\n> **Q: Is Olive's Garden a Mod / Modpack / Data Pack / Plugin...?**\n> \n> A: No, this is just a resource pack!\n\n> **Q: Can you / Will you make a Bedrock port?**\n> \n> A: To make a version that would work on Bedrock, I would need to learn how Bedrock works. So that's not something I plan to do any time soon for now, but it will come eventually.\n\n> **Q: Do you / Will you ever make a Mod?**\n> \n> A: We are currently working on a mod, follow us on ko-fi or patreon to stay up to date.\n\n> **Q: Can I put your resource pack in my Modpack?**\n> \n> A: Yes, you can do it as long as you give me credit.\n\n\n</details>",
